icy Institute of California  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aEnvironmental managementzCaliforniazDelta Region. 0aEstuarine ecologyzCaliforniazDelta Region. 0aWater diversionxEnvironmental aspectszCaliforniazDelta RegionxForecasting. 0aWater quality managementzCaliforniazDelta Region. 0aWater-supplyzCaliforniazDelta RegionxForecasting. 0aWater-supplyzCaliforniazDelta RegionxManagement. 7aNATURE / Ecology.2bisacsh1 aFleenor, William, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHanak, Ellen, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHowitt, Richard, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052094537140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520945371423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520945371/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles